{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1700-06_122", "resp": "wordpro"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "A Madame de Saliez, Viguiere d’Alby"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", juin 1700 [tome 6], p. 122-131."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "J’ajoute une Lettre du même M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[2]", "text": " de Vertron. La lecture vous en sera sans doute agreable."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "A MADAME"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[1]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[2]", "text": "DE SALIEZ,"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[2]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[3]", "text": "VIGUIERE D’ALBY,"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/lb[3]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "de l’Academie de Ricovrati."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "La forte attache que j’ay toûjours euë pour la belle gloire, m’a empêché d’en avoir beaucoup pour la Fortune. Cependant, Madame, "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "contre Fortune bon cœur"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/text()[2]", "text": ", c’est ma Devise dont j’ay fait remplir mes Numero à la Lotterie de Madame la Duchesse de Bourgogne. Virgile qui est de toute maniere "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/hi[2]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/hi[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Vates"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[1]/text()[3]", "text": ", me flate d’une agréable esperance du costé de la Cour, lieu où cette volage fait son sejour le plus long, parce qu’elle y vient tenir de temps en temps ses assises. Ce Prince des Poëtes Latins m’encourage par ce beau Vers,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Audaces fortuna juvat, timidosque repellit."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "“A luy faire la Cour elle veut qu’on s’attache."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Souvent un importun luy fait ouvrir les yeux ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Elle aide un cœur audacieux,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[1]/lg[2]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Et méprise toûjours le lâche,”"}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Les Epithetes dont les Orateurs & les Poëtes se servent contre cette Aveugle, montrent clairement la diversité de ses effets, ses injustices & ses caprices dans la distribution de ses largesses. Les noms de Hasard, d’Avanture, de Cas-fortuit, d’Evenement, d’Accident, de Rencontre, de Chance, d’Heur, d’Occasion, de Tour, de Coup, d’Etoile, d’Etat & de Changement, sont autant de sinonimes de la Fortune, & ce que les Stoïciens appelloient "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Fatum"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/text()[2]", "text": ", qui est le Destin ou la Destinée, c’est ce que nous appellons "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[2]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Sort"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/text()[3]", "text": ", j’oserois dire "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[3]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Lotterie"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/text()[4]", "text": " ; car enfin l’experience nous fait voir que les Lots dépendent de la Fortune, & que les billets blancs ou noirs viennent du "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[4]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/hi[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Sort"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[2]/text()[5]", "text": ". Les boëtes où l’on les met, & celles d’où on les tire, aprés les avoir bien tournez, sont des Cornes d’abondance pour les uns, & des balons remplis de vent pour les autres. Virgile qu’on ne sçauroit trop citer, exprime dans un Hemistiche, tout ce qu’on peut penser de la Lotterie."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[2]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Sors omnia versat."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Voicy comment j’ay étendu la pensée de cet admirable genie de l’Antiquité, qui parle de la Fortune en parlant du Sort."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "“A cette Aveugle Deïté"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Souvent la Justice s’oppose ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Son esprit de legereté"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[3]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "A son gré tourne toute chose…”"}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[4]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Quoy qu’il en soit, Madame, avoir ou n’avoir pas à la Loterie, ne decide point du merite ny du démerite des gens, mais seulement de leur bonheur ou de leur malheur. C’est ce qu’on nomme d’ordinaire bonne & mauvaise Fortune. Je souhaite qu’elle vous soit à l’avenir aussi favorable, qu’elle vous a esté contraire jusqu’à present."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "“Sçavante, aimable, & sage Brune,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous sçavez la raison pourquoy"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Je peste contre la Fortune ;"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais si chez la Princesse elle s’offroit à moy,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[4]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "J’employerois le gros Lot à servir un grand Roy.”"}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Sa Majesté qui n’avoit pas besoin de Louis, comme moy, en a pourtant gagné cinq à la Lotterie de l’Hôpital General. M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[5]/text()[2]", "text": " l’Abbé Peregrin de Marseille, dont vous avez vû plusieurs Ouvrages, vient de m’apporter une Epigramme qu’il a faite sur ce sujet. Remarquez, Madame, que le Roy a retiré trois cens cinq Louis, de trois cens qu’il avoit mis."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Cinq Louis ! "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "pour un Roy si grand !"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Sans doute le sort se méprend."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Cinq Louis ! "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[3]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[3]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Voicy le mistere :"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Les Petits-fils, le Fils, le Pere,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Sont compris dans ce nombre heureux."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "N’en jugeons plus sur l’apparence,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Cinq Louis "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[7]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[7]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "comblent tous nos vœux,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[5]/lg[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Et c’est le gros Lot de la France."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[6]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[6]/text()[1]", "text": "J’ay trouvé la pensée de cette Epigramme si nouvelle, que j’ay cru que je vous ferois plaisir de vous en envoyer une Copie dans sa nouveauté."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[7]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Sur le point de fermer ma Lettre, je viens d’apprendre qu’un des Gardes du Corps de Sa Majesté a gagné le gros Lot ; & en même temps un Capitaine aux Gardes de mes amis m’a fait la grace de m’apporter de Versailles ma boëte que j’ay ouverte en sa presence. Helas ! Madame, je ne suis pas plus heureux du costé de la Cour que du costé de la Ville, où j’ay perdu mon argent, & pour mieux dire, tout mon or, dans l’esperance de quelque aubaine ; mais"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]", "tag": "lg", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "“La Fortune "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "toûjours fut aveugle pour moy,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": " Et plus insensible qu’un buste."}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Je n’auray plus recours dans mes besoins qu’au Roy,"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": " "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[4]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[4]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Il est Fils de"}], "attributes": {"rend": "i"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/quote[6]/lg[1]/l[4]/text()[2]", "text": " Louis le Juste.”"}]}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[8]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Je vous ouvre mon cœur, comme à une bonne amie, qui entre genereusement dans mes interests ; car enfin, vous devez estre persuadée que j’entre même dans les vostres, & que je suis avec la derniere sincerité, Madame,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[9]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[9]/text()[1]", "text": "Vostre tres-humble, & tres-obéïssant serviteur, & tres-affectionné frere en Apollon "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[9]/lb[1]", "tag": "lb", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[9]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/p[9]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Ricovrato."}], "attributes": {"rend": "sc"}}]}]}]}